caption: We just found this place this morning and love it! They worked so hard to deliver our order, after we accidentally chose 'pickup' on their site, and they still got it to us within the hour! Great-tasting and high quality keto foods. The grilled cheese and tomato soup (my fave) was such a "treat" after 3 years on Keto! The chicken nuggets were made of high quality white meat, and the portion is very filling. Love the queso. My partner loved the cheese and egg tacos! He said it's exactly what he's tried to make himself - high praise from him!  Quick update: Mo and Dani worked so hard with us to make these amazing mini cheesecakes (just added to photos) that we special ordered for a tiny family wedding. They thought of everything and personally delivered our order!! Amazing couple and wonderful cheesecakes!

My husband and I ate breakfast here and it was so delicious! With us being gluten free, we often have troubles with cross contamination but not here. The staff was so friendly and helped us navigate the website. The website showed us all the different options offered and was super convenient!
It was amazing the food was fantastic and the staff they’re great , I am definitely coming here again!
As someone who never had Keto Food this was my first time and the Food was so delicious! Great atmosphere and a very friendly staff, the owner Mo is very easy to talk too!

This place was perfect for whether you are on keto, and even if you’re not!  We were driving from Des Moines to Chicago and I needed some keto food items. This was the perfect place to stock up!  They make it fresh to order, but I ate my blueberry donuts throughout the following week from the refrigerator and they were so amazing. Even when they were cold!  That plus the cinnamon bites were awesome and we are looking forward to trying the rest of the menu!  I highly recommend this place and we will definitely be stopping back here again when we are in the Iowa city area!
Great selection, friendly staff, and delicious food (especially the pizza & lasagna).  Look forward to trying more things on the menu!

I was traveling and looking for a restaurant and couldn't believe my eyes when I saw this place. If you've ever been on the keto diet you know how hard it is to find keto friendly menu options. I had to try it. When I got there the owner greeted me and was extremely personable and passionate. He recommended the lasagna, which was wonderful. He truly understands the ins and outs of the diet because he lives it himself. This place is what people on the diet have always wished existed

My first visit today for lunch.  I was thrilled to discover a restaurant in Iowa City that is focused on preparing and serving low carb food.  I tried the lasagne and the broccoli parm bake.  Both dishes were very tasty and satisfying,  I discovered low carb, vegetable focused (but I do eat red meat, poultry and fish as well) eating when I retired in 2016.  I lost 45 lbs. and never suffered from hunger pangs.  All of my test results at my annual physicals have been so much better and I haven't taken a prescription drug since I started following this course of eating.  The KETO Kitchen is unique in this area.  I no longer have to study a dish on the menu and figure out how the kitchen can modify it to keep the carb level low.  So, now we have a restaurant that serves delicious food that is low carb and provides an inviting and friendly atmosphere.  Kudos, Mo, for getting it right!

The Keto Kitchen is AMAZING!!!  I am so impressed with everything, I tried the lasagna, grilled cheese and tomato soup, Mac and cheese, garlic bread, salad, and donuts literally everything was fantastic!  As a foodie I was very skeptical, this is a place you can eat everyday!  Mo and his tram are fantastic, friendly and knowledgeable, if you are considering a Keto or Paleo lifestyle do yourself a favor and go to the Keto Kitchen, they will help you on your journey!

I eat gluten free a lot, and omg, the food was awesome!!! I can't believe there is a restaurant with gluten free options that taste this delicious!! I LOVED the nachos and there are  SO MANY toppings!!! I am hardcore considering the meal plan options they have, cuz I can definitely eat this food daily:)! Thank you guys for providing this option in Iowa City!!! Next time I have a family dinner I definitely plan to order a catered meal for my family!! Thank you The Keto Kitchen!!
BBQ drumsticks were fire!!!!

Whoa! Passing through and my husband found this GEM!!  The website is a bit tough to navigate, but do not let that deter you! Even if you are not keto, the food is delicious and the staff is friendly and helpful!  Let me HIGHLY recommend the Mac N Cheese!! That cheese sauce is AMAZING and creamy and rich! Will be back as often as my trips passing through Iowa City allow!

I work for a keto food blog and have a lot of familiarity with keto foods. I ordered the fat bombs to try which are a combination of chocolate and sunflower butter. They were creamy and smooth with a subtle nutty flavor that paired great with the chocolate. I was also able to meet a manager there as well as the creator of their fat bombs. Both of them were so kind and even gave me an in-depth explanation of why they choose the ingredients they did, and their promise to quality. I love seeing businesses who are so passionate about their craft and so kind to customers. I will definitely be back again to try a meal when they have their grand opening this month.

Awesome place!!!! It’s so hard to find healthy food, even in a city that claims to be health conscious and organic. This is ACTUALLY HEALTHY!!! I am gluten free and low carb and I’m in heaven. I definitely need to order the “Mac and cheese” next time. I got the risotto and it’s incredible! It’s cheesy and the cheese is kind of fried from the griddle. Sooooo good! I tried many things, all actually keto. None of that net carb nonsense claiming things like refried beans and rice are keto.  I tried: chicken nuggets, cauliflower risotto, broccoli parm, and brussle brittle. I would get them all again
Excellent food and great recommendations from the staff.  Very friendly.
Such an amazing, and educational experience!!! PLEASE TRY THE LASAGNA!!!! 10/10 would recommend to a friend!!  Ps  Try the lasagna
Great service and amazing food. I honestly feel this will be my new favorite spot to eat. I 100% recommend if you love healthy foods that taste good.
Oh my God, the food is so gross. I’m familiar with the keto diet, but this food is just awful. Spend your money someplace else, I threw most of the food out

Went to try this spot with my gf who is on the keto diet. I'm not vegan or keto or any of that so I wasn't expecting much from the food. Got the jumbo slider with egg and bacon and it was AMAZING! Definitely happy to find some healthier food that actually tastes great!
Get the steak. It'll make your day.

Amazing selection, amazing food, but most of all, amazing service. These guys are passionate about the keto lifestyle and love helping those that are just starting out. If you’re keto-curious, just getting started, or a long-time aficionado, this is your place!

This is the best keto experience I have ever had from any restaurant. The food is phenomenal. My entire family is on the keto diet and it's tough to find things to eat when we have to stay at hospital. The KETO Kitchen is bound to put a smile on your face no matter what you order.

This is our new spot! Amazing keto friendly food! I was so excited when this pulled up on my google search for keto foods! Finally a place where me and my family can go and eat that is healthy! The owners and the staff are wonderfully friendly! Best place I have ever been to eat with my family and will continue to go here for their yummy food!😍
Very good tasting not expensive at all
Very good food and great customer service! Would highly recommend, and will definitely eat here again.
The food is clearly made with actual love.

I recently grabbed dinner for my family and was surprised at the large variety they had to offer - the cauliflower risotto tasted amazing and I really couldn't believe all the desserts were Keto!! would 100 percent recommend to those wanting to try something new or trying to eat clean and healthy!

Neither of us is super strict with keto, but we do try to eat as low carb as possible. I'm also vegetarian, so eating out can be a challenge. This place had so many comfort food favorites to offer, and plenty of meat and veggie options. I loved the cauli mac and cheese, and my husband was really impressed with the lasagna and the lemon blueberry donuts. Really glad to have this option in town!

Although I'm not keto, I really wanted to try something new and The KETO Kitchen did not disappoint! I got the chicken nuggets, cauliflower risotto, and brussel sprout brittle --everything was super flavorful, unique, and came with good-sized portions for a good price. Dani is amazing in the kitchen!

Eating keto is something new to me. It's important for me to stay within my daily net carbs (approximately 23/day). The keto kitchen allows me to eat out, stay within my limits, and thrive in my new lifestyle.
Just tried this new place and the food is great! I’ll definitely be back!
Ever since I started the Keto diet, I have noticed a HUGE positive change in my overall mood, and gut health. The Fact that I now can get keto food on my way to campus or work is So great!  🙂

Trying Keto for the first time, wasn’t really sure what to expect. I ordered the nachos and they tasted pretty similar to what I’m used to which is really impressive. The delivery did take a little longer than expected but the food definitely made up for it ! 10/10 recommend and will be coming back!

I had my doubts about trying out the food here typically when I get something Keto it's flavorless, that was not my experience with the Keto Kitchen. I had the Mac & Cheese Cauliflower which was amazing a pepperoni pizza the meal left me satisfied from a flavor and hunger perspective. I would definatly recommend checking them out for great Keto food.
